{"id":47427,"slug":"saajan-ka-ghar","title":"Saajan Ka Ghar","title_hi":null,"year":"1994","type":"movie","plot":"The Dhanrajs are blessed with a daughter. However, during childbirth, Dhanraj's wife dies and he blames his daughter for his wife's fate. He refuses to see her face and remarries. His daughter, Laxmi, grows up to be a beautiful woman who's ignored by her father and abused by her stepmother. The only person who stands by her is her half-brother. Laxmi soon gets married but fate seems to hold nothing new for her. She has a loving relationship with her husband, but her mother-in-law couldn't stand her and she too physically abuses her.","plot_hi":null,"runtime":"153 min","rated":null,"language":null,"country":"IN","box_office":null,"awards":null,"imdb_id":"tt0173156","imdb_rating":null,"status":"published","image_url":"att0173156z.jpg","date_created":"2026-03-25T04:54:13.590Z","ratings":[{"source":"TMDB","value":"5.5/10"},{"source":"IMDb","value":"4.3/10"}],"genres":[{"id":9,"name":"Drama","slug":"drama"}],"cast":[{"id":1343,"name":"Rishi Kapoor","slug":"rishi-kapoor"},{"id":119807,"name":"Juhi Chawla Mehta","slug":"juhi-chawla-mehta"},{"id":59328,"name":"Deepak Tijori","slug":"deepak-tijori"},{"id":42069,"name":"Anupam Kher","slug":"anupam-kher"},{"id":71217,"name":"Kader Khan","slug":"kader-khan"},{"id":119811,"name":"Bindu Desai","slug":"bindu-desai"},{"id":66448,"name":"Alok Nath","slug":"alok-nath"},{"id":119113,"name":"Johny Lever","slug":"johny-lever"},{"id":119814,"name":"Dinesh Hingoo","slug":"dinesh-hingoo"},{"id":119815,"name":"Mohnish Behl","slug":"mohnish-behl"},{"id":119816,"name":"Tej Sapru","slug":"tej-sapru"}],"directors":[{"id":119817,"name":"Surendra Kumar Bohra","slug":"surendra-kumar-bohra"}],"writers":[],"recommendations":[{"id":47464,"slug":"hunting-season-1387382","title":"Hunting Season","title_hi":null,"year":"2025","type":"movie","imdb_rating":null,"image_url":"att32537226z.jpg"}],"updatedAt":"2026-03-26T05:16:19.796Z"}